Foxit Reader 9.0.0.29935 - 2017



FoxIt Reader- a professional program for viewing and printing documents in PDF format, an alternative to all known program Adobe Reader. A feature is the relatively small size of the distribution and fast work speed, which, undoubtedly, affects the convenience of the program as a whole. FoxIt Reader does not require a long-term installation. Presented product is not picky about the hardware and software computer and is able to work with all versions of Microsoft's operating systems, including those with Windows 8.

The program has all the necessary functions for a complete view PDF files. If you are tired of downloading PDF files for a few minutes and that the documents with graphics are scrolling too slowly, take a closer look at the alternative of Adobe Reader, the Foxit Reader program. This program has a very small size distribution, and it excludes all those unnecessary for most users options that make the program from Adobe slow and slow. Still, the main features are preserved: page-by-page viewing of files, quick navigation to the desired page, printing of documents. Foxit Reader pleasantly surprises with a simple and user-friendly interface.

 The program does not need installation, it is not demanding for software and system configuration of the computer and is able to work with almost all versions of Windows.
